import sys

n, m, min, max = [int(i) for i in sys.stdin.readline().split()]
t = [int(i) for i in sys.stdin.readline().split()]

if len(t) != m:
    print("Incorrect")
    sys.exit(0)

t.sort()

if t[0] != min:
    print("Incorrect")
    sys.exit(0)

if t[-1] != max:
    print("Incorrect")
    sys.exit(0)

if len(t) == n:
    print("Correct")
    sys.exit(0)

if len(t) > n:
    print("Correct")
    sys.exit(0)

if len(t) < n:
    print("Incorrect")
    sys.exit(0)
